R Notebook

library(tidyverse)
library(tidymodels)
library(DALEXtra)
set.seed(400)

Read Data

data_split <- readRDS(file = "../data/data_split.RData")
final_results <- readRDS(file = "../models/final_results.RData")
finalize_workflow_fitted <- final_results$.workflow[[1]]

Extract Training Data

data_train <- training(data_split)

features_train <- data_train %>% 
  select(bill_length_mm, 
         bill_depth_mm, 
         flipper_length_mm, 
         sex, 
         species)

labels_train <- data_train %>% select(body_mass_g)

data_train

Extract Test Data

data_test <- testing(data_split)
predictions_test <- finalize_workflow_fitted %>% predict(data_test)
Warning in predict.lm(object = object$fit, newdata = new_data, type = "response") :
  prediction from a rank-deficient fit may be misleading
data_test <- data_test %>%
  cbind(predictions_test)

data_test

Check for Bias

eval_metrics <- metric_set(rmse, rsq, mae)
data_test %>%
  group_by(sex) %>%
  eval_metrics(truth = body_mass_g, estimate = .pred)

Create Explainer

explainer_final <- finalize_workflow_fitted %>% 
  explain_tidymodels(
    data = features_train,
    y = labels_train[[1]]
  )
